Level 6
=======
Gets:
-----
* d6 HP
* +1 BAB
* +1 fort/ref saves
* +1 will save
* +1 2nd-level spell/day
* +3 3rd-level spells/day (+1 for ability score)
* 1 cantrip
* 1 third-level spell
* Favoured class bonus
* 1 spell swap

Actions:
--------
* Rolled 6 for HP!
* Favoured class bonus:- 1 skill point
* Cantrip - Dancing Lights
* New level 3 spell - Haste
* Spell swap Burning Hands -> Magic Missile
* 5 skill points:- UMD, Bluff, Intimidate x 2, Linguistics
* New language: Celestial

Current spell list:
-------------------
0: Acid Splash, Dancing Lights, Disrupt Indead, Mage Hand, Message, Prestidigitation, Read Magic
1: Chill Touch, Grease, Mage Armor, Magic Missile, Ray of Enfeeblement
2: Blindness-Deafness, False Life, Summon Monster II
3: Haste

